headline: TransDigm Expands Aftermarket Reach With Stellant And Jet Parts Deals
summary: TransDigm Group (NYSE:TDG) has agreed to acquire Stellant Systems, expanding its footprint in specialized aerospace components and systems. The company is also buying Jet Parts Engineering together with Victor Sierra Aviation, adding to its catalog of aftermarket-focused parts and services. Both deals are intended to deepen TransDigm Group's presence in the aerospace aftermarket and broaden its revenue streams. TransDigm Group comes into these acquisitions with a share price of $1,427.54...
